    d) Do one of the following:

        0) Convey the Minimal Corresponding Application Code under
        this License, or

        1) Convey the Minimal Corresponding Application Code under
        the GNU GPL, or

        2) Make the Minimal Corresponding Application Code available
        to anyone who requests it, under this License, for at least
